  * src/commands/Makefile.raw 1.1, src/commands/mmimport.raw 1.1, src/include/config.inc 1.2, src/include/config.raw 1.1, src/include/functions.inc 1.7, src/include/functions.raw 1.1, src/www/Makefile.raw 1.1, src/Documentation/Overview.txt 1.1, src/Makefile 1.1, src/README 1.5, src/changelog 1.1, src/config 1.1, src/configure 1.1, src/mmimport 1.3:
  Created a Makefile for convenience

  Added a file named "config". configure parses it and creates Makefiles
  and sed-scripts out of it's content.

  New Installation-Method:

   - vi config

   - make

   - make install
       as "root"

  Directory-Cleanup

